        <hl1>A Night With a Turtle</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Linda K Friedman letter on June 8 article recalls watching sea turtle lay eggs at Gumbo Limbo Environmental Complex in Boca Raton, Fla</p>
      </abstract>
